precis:
Amendments to the PEST CONTROL PRODUCTS REGULATIONS which will enable the
implementation of the Pesticide Own-Use Import Programme and allow
growers to import for their own use foreign-registered pesticides which
are chemically equivalent to Canadian-registered products.
